name: PICTURE DAY LTD by Gina Palmerin

metadata.name: Billie Byte - The Original
metadata.description: Welcome to the Picture Day – Limited Edition (1 of 1’s) masterfully hand crafted by oil based painter, Gina Palmerin and brought to the Metaverse as NFT's. These selected characters are Gina’s interpretation of them as elementary students. Each NFT of this series can be redeemed one time for the actual original oil based painting. Check our website for the physical claimed status. [www.vsnzlab.com](https://www.vsnzlab.com/)
